{"tid":627006,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"光速疑問","createTime":"2018-04-12T15:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T10:06:10.000Z","uid":150426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6854ecd12e6ad37206226b9f01804b41c286fa92","tid":627006,"uid":150426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"所有觀察者睇光速都係一樣姐條點？<br />\n點解光速係絕對？<br />\nTime dilation又關咩事？<br />\n<br />\n有無物理撚推廣科學"},{"pid":"8ba643393f28b2dacb57db5e28e7065e137b25a7","tid":627006,"uid":150426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所有觀察者睇光速都係一樣姐係點？<br />\n點解光速係絕對？<br />\nTime dilation又關咩事？<br />\n<br />\n有無物理撚推廣科學</blockquote>"},{"pid":"60924fc95701a57682194f888e4dfd3715c6a653","tid":627006,"uid":135132,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"首先，因為波需要有介質傳遞，例如海浪要水、聲音要空氣，光作為一種波應該都要有介質，當時假設該介質名為「以太」。<br />\n<br />\n「以太」被認為在宇宙中是無所不在的，太陽光才能傳送到地球。但地球會圍著太陽公轉，即理應會在「以太」中前進，在介質中移動，接收到的波會有分別，日常例子就是警車聲向自己移動和遠離是不同的。為了找出光在「以太」中移動的速度，建立了邁克生-莫雷實驗，研究在不同方向的光會有甚麼的速度變化。<br />\n<br />\n實驗結果：光速在任何方向量度都是<span style=\"color: gold;\">相同的</span>。亦即是「以太」不存在，光可以不需要介質傳遞。"},{"pid":"0f7fa793425cc58673657ea487163c978fc981b9","tid":627006,"uid":150426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"好似無答到條問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552fb8a28f83c9475be7ed89723c21b50ffed44b","tid":627006,"uid":135132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f7fa793425cc58673657ea487163c978fc981b9","tid":627006,"uid":150426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"好似無答到條問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"一次講唔哂俾少少耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfac12abf7e118cb80b4dcade3436a11c1d301a","tid":627006,"uid":135132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"16世紀時已經有定論光速並非無限，而光是電磁波，物理撚馬克士威提出上限為c。結合上面實驗結果，愛因斯坦假設光速是獨立於觀察者，有不變的速度c，並依據此假設建立相對論。<br />\n<br />\n從相對論中推導出的e=mc^2質能等價公式，表示了愈接近光速，需要的能量愈接近無限大。因此光速是<span style=\"color: gold;\">所有運動的速度上限</span>。"},{"pid":"bdc257271ce8faf6f772125e19a0d822bce5a93f","tid":627006,"uid":135132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"因為實驗證明了光速在地球運動的各個方向都是相等的，而除了用高密度介質減慢光速外（小學都學過的折射原理），並無法反證光速<span style=\"color: red;\">不是絕對</span>，因此光速不變原理是一個公設：光速於任何參考系中都一樣速度。<br />\n<br />\n建基在光速不變，任何觀測者觀測到的光速都相等，因此引伸出時間膨脹理論，去片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=X61cRz_1wGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX61cRz_1wGg&d=tcVB8DBkPI5NzQNp5hlX66EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=63b78e74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=X61cRz_1wGg</a>"},{"pid":"417e01cf2d658a5e3aa9721abce0e4e19c217893","tid":627006,"uid":135132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"Between，光速不變無原因，就是一個定律<br />\n<br />\n其實全部維基都有講，仲好詳細添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893b5a94c9520045ed909c87e870eae5836de476","tid":627006,"uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"417e01cf2d658a5e3aa9721abce0e4e19c217893","tid":627006,"uid":135132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"Between，光速不變無原因，就是一個定律<br />\n<br />\n其實全部維基都有講，仲好詳細添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"我會話係一個現象多過定律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d909c7d1e044329610d6b7e5831426ddb40e8a0","tid":627006,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid